{"tid":2100163,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"甄子丹首度擔正演荷里活新片　繼《追龍》後演跨國大毒梟","createTime":"2020-07-09T00:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T05:00:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5032283cad58eb5f9b9c2fc13ed42808548e7fac","tid":2100163,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"有「宇宙最強」之稱的甄子丹再衝出香港，迎來事業另一高峰，據外媒報導，甄子丹將主演荷里活犯罪驚悚電影《Golden Empire》（暫譯：《黃金帝國》），飾演一個大毒梟，是美國和墨西哥政府的頭號通緝犯。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒《Deadline》報道，現年56歲的甄子丹繼在2017年的電影《追龍》演過大毒梟，今次在荷里活新片《Golden Empire》（暫譯：《黃金帝國》）中，將會演出一個臭名遠播的跨國大毒品集團大佬。除了在《Golden Empire》演出，據知甄子丹更會有份製作，與製片人Peter Luo合作。<br />\n<br />\n而製片人Peter Luo也表示，這部電影是第一部由亞洲演員主演，目標是全球觀眾，有關毒品題材的大片，「對白是英語，電影主要拍攝地會在美國，劇情會橫跨亞洲、北美和南美。」<br />\nPeter Luo透露自己是因為看過甄子丹在《追龍》的演出後，認為他就是《Golden Empire》主角最適合的人選。<br />\n<br />\n其實，甄子丹近年都非常積極進軍荷里活，演出《星球大戰外傳：俠盜一號》，成為首個演出《星球大戰》系列的亞洲演員，上映後也獲不錯評價。<br />\n甄子丹也在《3X反恐暴族：重火力回歸》與雲迪素合作，以及在《花木蘭》也有演出。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，甄子丹最近也在社交媒體上公布，自己要為下一個挑戰做準備，更標籤了「#Sleepingdog」、「#actionmovie」，原來丹爺將會演出《Sleeping Dogs》真人電影版。<br />\n被稱為「港版 GTA」的開放世界動作遊戲《Sleeping Dogs》，在2012年由United Front Games所製作，以香港為背景的臥底的那段故事，十分經典。<br />\n<br />\n《Sleeping Dogs》2012年由Square Enix發行的動作冒險遊戲，當年更找來陳冠希等明星配音，玩家在遊戲中扮演一名叫沈威的臥底警察，深入險惡的香港三合會組織，揭露背後的各種陰謀。甄子丹公開將會接拍這部真人版電影後，不少網民都表示很興奮。<br />\n<br />\n甄子丹最近就透露，他即將出演《Sleeping Dogs》遊戲改編的真人電影 《Sleeping Dogs》，電影將由曾出品《超音鼠》電影的製片公司 dj2 Entertainment 監製。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1505152/org/56b827f63b179c420431ade7dda20c37.jpg/jXSHZ6_xC0zs_L6h3iw4YFHe5dTLqan75M2LPuTNiz4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1505152%2Forg%2F56b827f63b179c420431ade7dda20c37.jpg%2FjXSHZ6_xC0zs_L6h3iw4YFHe5dTLqan75M2LPuTNiz4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=5aa733c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73b84747fa44a8cb33fee2764bc2f83ab3fd1505","tid":2100163,"uid":64953,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:39:33.000Z","msg":"Sleeping dogs 套戲都聽咗幾年<br />\n佢仲打唔打得郁"},{"pid":"f55f1fcfac2362f86b5c4403665b1d0bb38d8448","tid":2100163,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:40:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af4187b3a6bea7160cb9739d69fb2f66dc762dcd","tid":2100163,"uid":83328,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:41:16.000Z","msg":"So 辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968f3276329d35bb7d823315b0f203d5a7ebf541","tid":2100163,"uid":56731,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:41:53.000Z","msg":"東亞病夫"},{"pid":"6449caeefb577fa09f5a31f97a8f695749806bfe","tid":2100163,"uid":68689,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:42:04.000Z","msg":"等我比你知道咩係眼前一黑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9c924954aa9cf3ed87e40b27e000c548dd430d","tid":2100163,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:43:48.000Z","msg":"老恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382e6141fd2dd482e5d7b34c1017e86075c71bde","tid":2100163,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:44:12.000Z","msg":"拍中資片就夠啦<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"eb747d80411427274d40fa0ace24734ba1f960d8","tid":2100163,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:46:50.000Z","msg":"佢就發啦，又有得突破洋腸嘞🇺🇸🇲🇽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab041213e825aa55077a1ebe2a98d71e53c0d5c","tid":2100163,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:02:18.000Z","msg":"世界毒瘤"},{"pid":"1203c6c2b43617c8f6d9dd2632d9236a89a3753b","tid":2100163,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"